{"list":[{"title":"目的","data":"<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\">知道钠与水反应的现象和原理。</span></p>"},{"title":"原理","data":"<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman'\">2Na + 2H</span><sub><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman'\">2</span></sub><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman'\">O = 2NaOH + H</span><sub><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman'\">2</span></sub><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman'\">&uarr;</span></span></span></p>"},{"title":"用品","data":"<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman'\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">仪器：镊子、滤纸、小刀、烧杯。</span></span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">药品：钠、蒸馏水、酚酞。</span></span></p>"},{"title":"步骤","data":"<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman'\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">取一块金属钠，用滤纸吸干表面的煤油，然后用小刀切下一小块，</span></span><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">剩余的钠放回瓶中</span></span><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman'\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">。</span></span><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">在烧杯中倒入一些蒸馏水，然后滴加几滴酚酞</span></span><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman'\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">，</span></span><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">将钠放入烧杯中，</span></span><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman'\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">观察实验现象。</span></span></span></span></p>"},{"title":"现象","data":"<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">钠浮在水面上（浮），熔成小球（熔）并在水面快速移动（游），发出嘶嘶的响声（响），溶液变红（红）。</span></span></span></span></p>"}],"x":0,"y":0,"width":600,"height":600}